   <pre><code>helm upgrade --install --namespace expertflow --create-namespace   ef-cx  --debug --values helm-values/ef-cx-custom-values.yaml expertflow/cx --version 4.10.2 
</code></pre>
  </div>
 </scroll-shadow>
 <copy-clipboard class="theme-code-snippet-copy">
  <svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" data-component="icon" class="icon icon-copy_content copy-icon">
   <use href="/__theme/b_8ca5a7d7-80f3-41c8-bea7-75cce14ad14f/scroll-sites-help-center-theme/41/icons.svg#copy_content"></use>
  </svg>
 </copy-clipboard>
</code-snippet>
<p>“ef-cx” in the above command is the release name which will be referenced in all subsequent functional groups' deployments.</p>
