 <div class="expand-body">
  <p>You must first create custom <code>values.yaml</code> file to define your minimum required configurations.</p>
  <h4 id="Step-1:-Create-the-Values-File.2"><span id="UpgradeguideCX4.4.10toCX4.10.2-Step1:CreatetheValuesFile"></span>Step 1: Create the Values File
