     </svg>
    </copy-clipboard>
   </i18n-message></h4>
  <p>You can extend the same <code>cx-channels-custom-values.yaml</code> file with additional configurations as needed, including environment variables, replica counts, etc.</p>
  <p>To view all available default configurations and decide what you want to override:</p>
  <code-snippet class="theme-code-snippet">
   <scroll-shadow>
